description:
The ZUNTATA Music Pack featuring arrangements of Touhou songs by TAITO's sound team ZUNTATA has arrived!
You can now enjoy long versions of Groove Coaster songs exclusively for Spell Bubble!
Shohei Tsuchiya takes on Touhou arrangements for the first time!
Believe it or not, all songs will be new arrangements or brand new songs!

Don't miss out on this great opportunity to enjoy these catchy tunes on Spell Bubble!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・Touhou Onganmu / COSIO
・Touhou Sangakusai / COSIO
・Touhou Gaimaden / MASAKI (ZUNTATA)
・Touhou Kijinretsu / MASAKI (ZUNTATA)
・Touhou Sei REN-SEN / MASAKI (ZUNTATA)
・The Gensokyo the Gods Loved ST MIX / Shohei Tsuchiya (ZUNTATA)

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 The Game I Fell For (The Gensokyo the Gods Loved ST MIX)
・Lv.6 Part-time Guard (Touhou Sangakusai)
・Lv.7 Blasting Music (Touhou Onganmu)
・Lv.8 Without Honor and Humanity (Touhou Kijinretsu)
・Lv.9 Hot Streak? (Touhou Sei REN-SEN)
・Lv.10 Does Marisa Know? (Touhou Gaimaden)

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: ZUNTATA Music Pack
